# Synapse Harness Weekly Audit — Cron Configuration
# ----------------------------------------------------------------
# Activates the weekly Harness audit every Sunday 23:00 Dubai (= 19:00 UTC)
# Per president 2026-04-27 decision ②A weekly review activation.
#
# Linux server activation:
#   crontab -e
#   <paste the line below, adjust path to your Synapse-Mini clone>
#
# Windows Task Scheduler activation (alternative):
#   - Trigger: Weekly, Sunday, 23:00 (Asia/Dubai)
#   - Action:  python -X utf8 "C:\Users\<user>\Synapse-Mini\agent-CEO\dispatch_weekly_audit.py"
#
# Output report path:
#   obs/01-team-knowledge/HR/weekly-audit/week-audit-YYYY-WXX.md
#
# Failure escalation:
#   - 1 missed week  -> Lysander dispatches harness_engineer to backfill
#   - 2 missed weeks -> L4 president escalation

# Sunday 23:00 Dubai = Sunday 19:00 UTC
0 19 * * 0 cd /home/lysanderl/Synapse-Mini && python3 -X utf8 agent-CEO/dispatch_weekly_audit.py >> logs/weekly-audit.log 2>&1
